{"word":"G339 - ἀνακαθίζω - anakathízō - an-ak-ath-id'-zo - Sit up","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνακαθίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anakathízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ak-ath-id'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Sit up</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"உட்கார் - செய்யப்படுபொருள்"},{"paragraph":"to raise oneself and sit upright, to sit up, sit erect"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G303 - ἀνά - aná - an-ah'/303\">G303</a> and <a href=\"#/G2523 - καθίζω - kathízō - kath-id'-zo/2523\">G2523</a>; properly to <i>set up</i>, that is, (reflexively) to <i>sit up:</i> - sit up.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}